ation that due to their lower compressive\nstrength they reach hydrostatic equlibrium at smaller sizes than their inner\nsolar system counterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 20:18:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
