ation between the size of the bump feature\nand $\\beta_{XY, 1}$ can be understood as a result of chemical mixing due to\nlarge-scale Rayleigh-Taylor instabilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 04:04:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2022 18:15:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 May 2023 18:50:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
