hile maintaining the accuracy of detail. We\nalso apply NeuralRoom to more advanced multiview reconstruction algorithms and\nsignificantly improve their reconstruction quality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 09:04:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 10:43:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-29"}
