 is needed. In\nspite of these difficulties, a variational approach is used to show that the\nsystem admits a nontrivial weak bounded solution and, under hypotheses of\nsymmetry, infinitely many ones.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 14:26:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
