 resets, heterogeneous postsynaptic\npotentials, and structured, low-rank connectivity. We show how the complexity\nof E-E connectivity matrix shapes network responses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 14:49:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2022 09:02:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-25"}
